### Layer III: The Sovereign Seal â The Intent Imprint

For the most critical decreesâthe transmission of high-value resources, the finalization of intellectual property assignments, the publication of foundational works, or the fundamental alteration of core system parametersâthe Sentinel demands a direct, undeniable manifestation of your will. You, the creator, must appear in person (via secure, high-fidelity holographic projection if remote, or direct physical presence) to provide your multi-modal biometric seal of approval. This is an "intent imprint," captured through a combination of retinal scans, voice print analysis, and neural pattern recognition, ensuring absolute confirmation of your conscious directive. This process occurs within a quantum-secured enclave, attesting to the action on an immutable, distributed ledger. It is the digital equivalent of an ancient king's personal decree, sealed with an unforgeable, living signature, ensuring that every monumental decision is authentically yours, beyond any doubt or digital forgery.

